org.hypergraphdb.query.impl

Class HandleArrayResultSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hypergraphdb.query.impl.HandleArrayResultSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.util.Iterator<HGHandle>, HGSearchResult<HGHandle>, TwoWayIterator<HGHandle>, CloseMe

    public class HandleArrayResultSet
extends java.lang.Object
implements HGSearchResult<HGHandle>

    Implements a HGSearchResult comprising the atoms in a given HGHandle array.

    Note: this is not an ordered result set, but can easily be made so if this proves beneficial.
